text: Lansana Conté (30 November 1934 – 22 December 2008"Guinea's long-time military leader Conte dies", AFP, 23 December 2008.) was a Guinean politician and military official. He was the second President of Guinea, from 3 April 1984 until his death on 22 December 2008. Conté came to power in the 1984 Guinean coup d'état. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Presidents of Guinea
title: Lansana Conté
